n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">社区成员可以建议对维基进行更改或纠正，以保持内容的准确性和完整性。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">项目通过多种渠道（如 Discord）接收用户贡献，促进资源发现与共享。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">benman1/generative_ai_with_langchain</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/benman1/generative_ai_with_langchain\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/benman1/generative_ai_with_langchain</a></span></span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stars:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: a